The paper discusses resource scheduling in infrastructure as a service (IaaS) for large-scale Cloud applications, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions network infrastructure and environment, which suggests the category of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The comparison of simulators and their performance metrics falls under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE). The discussion on scalability and future research trends suggests the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Platform-Based Development (cs.PF).
